---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base
  title="Learn Vim in your browser"
  description="Free, interactive Vim lessons and tips that run entirely in your browser."
>
  <article>
    <h1>Learn Vim in your browser.</h1>
    <p>
      vimmer.io is a free collection of Vim lessons and tips. Lessons are short,
      hands-on, and (eventually) run a real Vim instance compiled to WebAssembly
      right here on the page — no install required.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="/lessons">Start with the lessons</a>, or browse a
      <a href="/tips">pile of tips</a> for things you may not have known Vim
      could do.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
